---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Formik Multi-Step Forms for Enterprise React | Validation Guide"
  description="Formik multi-step form implementation with Yup validation from TESCO Stores CZ operations portal."
>
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col gap-12">
    <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="text-sm text-slate-400">
      <a href="/" class="transition hover:text-accent">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-2">→</span>
      <a href="/vocabulary" class="transition hover:text-accent">Vocabulary</a>
      <span class="mx-2">→</span>
      <span class="text-slate-200">Formik Multi-Step Forms</span>
    </nav>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <p class="eyebrow">Forms & Validation</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white sm:text-5xl">Formik Multi-Step Forms</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300">Complex workflow wizards with Yup validation</p>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-[32px] border border-accent/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-transparent p-8 shadow-card">
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-100">
        <strong class="text-white">Definition:</strong> Formik is a declarative form library for React enabling complex multi-step wizards with Yup schema validation, ideal for enterprise workflows requiring step-by-step data collection.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="surface-card space-y-6">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Multi-Step Patterns</h2>
      </div>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-200">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Wizard navigation:</strong> Progress indicators and step validation</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Per-step validation:</strong> Yup schemas ensure data quality</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">State persistence:</strong> Save progress across sessions</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Conditional steps:</strong> Dynamic workflows based on user input</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="surface-card space-y-6">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow text-accent">Case Study</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Real Implementation: TESCO</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-200">
        The <strong class="text-white">TESCO operations portal</strong> uses Formik for complex campaign planning forms with multi-step workflows, conditional validation, and Material UI integration.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Related Vocabulary</h3>
      <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <a href="/vocabulary/react-hook-form" class="grid-panel">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-accent">React Hook Form</h4>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Alternative performant form library</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/vocabulary/material-ui-design-system" class="grid-panel">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-accent">Material UI Design System</h4>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">UI components for forms</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-[32px] border border-accent/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-transparent p-8 text-center shadow-card">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Need Complex Forms?</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-slate-200">I build multi-step forms with Formik and React Hook Form for enterprise workflows.</p>
      <a href="mailto:marekdolnicek@gmail.com" class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-full bg-accent px-8 py-3 font-semibold text-ink shadow-card transition hover:bg-accentMuted">Contact me</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
